        "html":  "\u003cdiv class=\"card\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e渐变边框\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是一个带有动态渐变边框的卡片效果。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
        "css":  "body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;background:#0d0d0d;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:sans-serif}.card{position:relative;width:300px;padding:30px;background:#1a1a2e;border-radius:16px;color:#fff;z-index:1}.card::before{content:\u0027\u0027;position:absolute;inset:-2px;background:linear-gradient(45deg,#667eea,#764ba2,#f093fb,#f5576c);border-radius:18px;z-index:-1;animation:rotate 3s linear infinite;background-size:400% 400%}.card::after{content:\u0027\u0027;position:absolute;inset:0;background:#1a1a2e;border-radius:16px;z-index:-1}@keyframes rotate{0%{background-position:0% 50%}50%{background-position:100% 50%}100%{background-position:0% 50%}}h2{margin:0 0 15px}p{color:#aaa;margin:0;line-height:1.6}",
        "js":  "",
        "authorName":  "Web Effect Studio",
        "viewCount":  0,
